---
// src/components/home/StepsSection.astro
---
<section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 pt-16 pb-8">
  <div class="text-center mb-12">
    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-slate-800" style="font-family: var(--font-heading);">
      Primeiros Passos Para Nova Renda
    </h2>
    <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-slate-500 max-w-2xl mx-auto font-medium">
      Siga este caminho simples e escale seus resultados com o nosso sistema de recrutamento automático.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
    <!-- Passo 1 -->
    <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 border border-slate-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 text-center flex flex-col items-center">
      <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-indigo-50 text-indigo-500 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
        <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 20l-5.447-2.724A1 1 0 013 16.382V5.618a1 1 0 011.447-.894L9 7m0 13l6-3m-6 3V7m6 10l4.553 2.276A1 1 0 0021 18.382V7.618a1 1 0 00-.553-.894L15 4m0 13V4m0 0L9 7" />
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-3" style="font-family: var(--font-heading);">
        Passo 1: Conhecer o Plano
      </h3>
      <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed text-sm">
        Descubra como a nossa oportunidade funciona, entendendo todos os detalhes do plano e o incrível potencial de ganhos.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Passo 2 -->
    <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 border border-slate-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 text-center flex flex-col items-center relative">
      <!-- Seta indicativa (escondida no mobile) -->
      <div class="hidden md:block absolute -left-6 top-[30%] text-slate-300">
        <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="3" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
        </svg>
      </div>
      <div class="hidden md:block absolute -right-6 top-[30%] text-slate-300 z-10">
        <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="3" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
        </svg>
      </div>

      <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-amber-50 text-amber-500 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
        <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-3" style="font-family: var(--font-heading);">
        Passo 2: Ativação e Estratégia
      </h3>
      <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed text-sm">
        Faça sua ativação de forma rápida e segura para receber o mapa estratégico exato focado no seu posicionamento.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Passo 3 -->
    <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 border border-slate-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 text-center flex flex-col items-center">
      <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-emerald-50 text-emerald-500 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
        <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-3" style="font-family: var(--font-heading);">
        Passo 3: Gerar Nova Renda
      </h3>
      <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed text-sm">
        Comece a usar nosso sistema automático com <strong>funil completo:</strong> anúncio, captura de leads, CRM, automação, duplicação e escala!
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="mt-12 text-center">
    <a href="https://wa.me/5591981992265" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 bg-[#25D366] hover:bg-[#1DA851] text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-full text-lg font-bold transition-transform hover:-translate-y-1 shadow-lg shadow-[#25D366]/30">
      <svg class="w-6 h-6 fill-current" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M17.472 14.382c-.297-.149-1.758-.867-2.03-.967-.273-.099-.471-.148-.67.15-.197.297-.767.966-.94 1.164-.173.199-.347.223-.644.075-.297-.15-1.255-.463-2.39-1.475-.883-.788-1.48-1.761-1.653-2.059-.173-.297-.018-.458.13-.606.134-.133.298-.347.446-.52.149-.174.198-.298.298-.497.099-.198.05-.371-.025-.52-.075-.149-.669-1.612-.916-2.207-.242-.579-.487-.5-.669-.51a12.8 12.8 0 0 0-.57-.01c-.198 0-.52.074-.792.372-.272.297-1.04 1.016-1.04 2.479 0 1.462 1.065 2.875 1.213 3.074.149.198 2.096 3.2 5.077 4.487.709.306 1.262.489 1.694.625.712.227 1.36.195 1.871.118.571-.085 1.758-.719 2.006-1.413.248-.694.248-1.289.173-1.413-.074-.124-.272-.198-.57-.347m-5.421 7.403h-.004a9.87 9.87 0 0 1-5.031-1.378l-.361-.214-3.741.982.998-3.648-.235-.374a9.86 9.86 0 0 1-1.51-5.26c.001-5.45 4.436-9.884 9.888-9.884 2.64 0 5.122 1.03 6.988 2.898a9.825 9.825 0 0 1 2.893 6.994c-.003 5.45-4.437 9.884-9.885 9.884m8.413-18.297A11.815 11.815 0 0 0 12.052 0C5.495 0 .16 5.335.157 11.892c0 2.096.547 4.142 1.588 5.945L.057 24l6.305-1.654a11.882 11.882 0 0 0 5.683 1.448h.005c6.554 0 11.89-5.335 11.893-11.893a11.821 11.821 0 0 0-3.48-8.413Z"/></svg>
      Quero Começar Agora!
    </a>
  </div>
</section>
